---
title: Sweet and Smoky Grilled Chicken with Slaw, Corn and Honey-Chive Butter
description: Applewood BBQ seasoning and honey are a lip-smacking combo, especially on grilled chicken! Crunchy coleslaw and juicy corn on the cob elevate this dish to summer perfection.
image: https://img.hellofresh.com/f_auto,fl_lossy,h_640,q_auto,w_1200/hellofresh_s3/image/poulet-grille-doux-et-fume-561bf7d5.jpg
